## 3. Data Sources

All data from HKO Open Data API. No third-party dependencies.

### 3.1 Real-time Feeds (polled every 15 min)

| Agent | Endpoint | Key Fields |
|---|---|---|
| RainfallAgent | `hourlyRainfall.php?lang=en` | `hourlyRainfall[].value` per station |
| TideAgent | `opendata.php?dataType=HHOT&station=QUB` | Hourly tide heights (Quarry Bay — reference gauge) |
| TideAgent (secondary) | `opendata.php?dataType=HHOT&station=TBT` | Tsim Bei Tsui — NT west coast |
| TideAgent (secondary) | `opendata.php?dataType=HHOT&station=CCH` | Cheung Chau — south waters |
| WarningAgent | `weather.php?dataType=warnsum` | Active warning codes + action codes |
| WarningAgent | `weather.php?dataType=warningInfo` | Full warning text (semantic content) |
| ForecastAgent | `weather.php?dataType=fnd` | PSR, forecastMaxRH, forecastWind |
| ForecastAgent | `weather.php?dataType=flw` | generalSituation, tclnfo, outlook |
| LightningAgent | `opendata.php?dataType=LHL&rformat=json` | Cloud-to-ground count per district |

### 3.2 Tide Stations Coverage Strategy

We use three tide gauges to cover HK's three flood vulnerability zones:

- **QUB (Quarry Bay)** — Victoria Harbour / urban core / MTR tunnel risk
- **TBT (Tsim Bei Tsui)** — Deep Bay / northern NT / Yuen Long plains (historically most flood-prone)
- **CCH (Cheung Chau)** — South Lamma Channel / storm surge from typhoons from the south

### 3.3 Rainfall Station → District Mapping

The 35 AWS stations in `hourlyRainfall.php` are mapped to HK's 18 districts:

```json
{
  "Yuen Long": ["RF001", "RF002", "N12"],
  "Tuen Mun": ["RF019"],
  "North": ["RF015", "RF016", "RF017"],
  "Tai Po": ["RF004", "RF005"],
  "Sha Tin": ["RF020"],
  "Sai Kung": ["RF006", "RF007", "N15"],
  "Eastern": ["RF008", "RF009", "RF026"],
  "Islands": ["RF010", "RF011", "RF012", "RF013", "RF014"],
  "Kwun Tong": ["K03", "RF008"],
  "Kowloon City": ["RF025"],
  "Sham Shui Po": ["RF022"],
  "Yau Tsim Mong": ["K02"],
  "Wong Tai Sin": ["RF025", "K09"],
  "Kwai Tsing": ["RF018", "RF021"],
  "Tsuen Wan": ["RF018"],
  "Central & Western": ["RF023", "RF027"],
  "Wan Chai": ["RF027", "H17"],
  "Southern": ["H15", "H24", "RF028"]
}
```

