## 11. Implementation Roadmap

### Phase 1 — Foundation (Week 1–2)

- [ ] Scaffold agent base class with `fetch()`, `analyse()`, `handlePeerQuery()` interface
- [ ] Implement HKO API clients for all 9 endpoints with retry logic
- [ ] Build `RainfallAgent` — simplest to validate (direct numerical → score)
- [ ] Build `WarningAgent` — validates the warning code parsing + text extraction
- [ ] Implement `AgentSignal` schema + JSON validation
- [ ] Build basic `SynthesisAgent` (no compound detection yet)
- [ ] End-to-end smoke test with live HKO data

### Phase 2 — Full Swarm (Week 3–4)

- [ ] Build `TideAgent` with multi-gauge reasoning
- [ ] Build `ForecastAgent` with PSR semantic interpretation
- [ ] Build `LightningAgent` with cell movement inference
- [ ] Implement peer query protocol (message passing between agents)
- [ ] Build `CompoundDetector` with full flag taxonomy
- [ ] Upgrade `SynthesisAgent` to consume compound flags
- [ ] Implement `OrchestratorAgent` with timeout/retry logic
- [ ] Add station→district mapping module

### Phase 3 — Output & Observability (Week 5–6)

- [ ] Implement bilingual narrative generation (EN + TC)
- [ ] Build `FloodAlertOutput` full schema
- [ ] Add run logging + audit trail (every run saved to JSON)
- [ ] Build simple dashboard (React) showing live agent signals + alert level
- [ ] Implement regression test harness with 10 historical events

### Phase 4 — Benchmarking (Week 7–8)

- [ ] Build ML baselines (logistic regression + LSTM) on historical data
- [ ] Run all 3 systems against historical event set
- [ ] Compute CSI, FAR, POD, compound detection rate
- [ ] Produce comparison report
- [ ] Tune synthesis weights based on evaluation results

